text: Aey yousuf! Aey boht baray sachay yousuf! Aap humen iss khuwab ki tabeer batlaiye kay saat moti taza gayen hain jinhen saat dubli patli gayen kha rahi hain aur saat bilkul sabz khoshay hain aur saat hi doosray bhi bilkul khushk hain takay mein wapis jaa ker unn logon say kahon kay woh sab jaan len
